gitmap clone-now: dry-run
source: <SOURCE> (<FORMAT>, mode=https)
2 row(s) -- pass --execute to actually clone

  [1/2] widget
        url:    https://github.com/acme/widget.git
        dest:   acme/widget
        branch: main
  [2/2] gadget
        url:    https://github.com/acme/gadget.git
        dest:   acme/gadget
        branch: develop
